as an aside FizzBuzz in Spoken Python

function fizzbuzz parameters with n
    for i in range with n
        if i modulo 15 equals 0
            print with string literal FizzBuzz
        else if i modulo 3 equals 0
            print with string literal Fizz
        else if i modulo 5 equals 0
            print with string literal Buzz
        else
            print with string literal other
        close if
    close for
close function

fizzbuzz with 100
